    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-02-15">15 February 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/war-disablement-pension-rates-2019">War disablement pension rates 2019</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The 2019 war disablement pension rates have been announced.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
